Prager 20140218  1 Woody Allen

Prager H1: Dennis has taken no position on the Woody Allen/Dylan Farrow controversy.
             But he does have a position on the self-destructive impulse
              to believe that your life has been destroyed by some bad incident in your past.
               Without excusing any hideous behavior Woody Allen may have engaged in,
                if it did happen it happened 26 years ago

           Dennis talks to Ann McElhinney,
